    General Stores in Malad, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Depending on the location of the store  whether in a rural village or an urban metropolis  the stock keeping units or pack sizes of the packaged goods may differ. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Malad, Mumbai from the list given above.
